The '''133rd Imperial Fighter Group''' was a [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Flight group/Legends|group]] that was attached to the [[Fleet/Legends|fleet]] of [[Xandel Carivus]] during his stint as the head of the [[Imperial Ruling Council/Legends|Imperial Interim Ruling Council]]. The 133rd fought during [[Battle of Ord Cantrell|their battle]] against the forces of [[Baron/Legends|Baron]] [[Ragez D'Asta]].

